i\" /> <br />\n<br />\n茶都係，飲到厭左可以換過第二隻茶繼續嘆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/014009_6bcec4451c8785c539700d5b224a6246.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F014009_6bcec4451c8785c539700d5b224a6246.png&h=f095b469&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7df4810f987694831abaa33480bc1c9f68866c23","tid":806373,"uid":132470,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:53:39.000Z","msg":"我上次去Claridge&rsquo;s<br />\n貴 倫敦數一數二最高檔tea<br />\n講緊係&pound;60一位 未計service charge<br />\n但係 由服務到食物到茶<br />\n都係非常非常之出色<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/014816_a1462b478fe6262a014f1a44a3a3d52c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F014816_a1462b478fe6262a014f1a44a3a3d52c.png&h=339f6995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我本身勁討厭三文治兼對所有包類冇興趣<br />\n但係竟然三文治食咗兩碟<br />\n甜品款唔多 每日只供應4款<br />\n但係非常精緻 食哂四件都唔覺漏<br />\n味道配搭得好好<br />\n<br />\n到tea 我諗起碼有40種茶 有詳細介紹 你可以拎住menu慢慢揀<br />\n<br />\n杯碟全部都係customized，tableware係銀造<br />\n<br />\n另外 我搵資料時係參考左呢個blog<br />\n寫得好好 博主試勻英撚多間下午茶 <br />\n好值得參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/monologuebytom.net/2016/02/22/claridges-afternoon-tea-倫敦最棒的英式下午茶/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fmonologuebytom.net%2F2016%2F02%2F22%2Fclaridges-afternoon-tea-%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E6%9C%80%E6%A3%92%E7%9A%84%E8%8B%B1%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%88%E8%8C%B6%2Famp%2F&d=Z0I2R6kT1vvKUY1NmPO7MbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=ef855712\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/monologuebytom.net/2016/02/22/claridges-afternoon-tea-倫敦最棒的英式下午茶/amp/</a>"},{"pid":"180d355a128f7bcb453896741c4290a6396d4143","tid":806373,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T23:39:02.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"31430bf